{"tid":936346,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［歧黃之術］召集連登對中醫藥有認識既朋友！","createTime":"2018-12-10T16:26:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T10:50:07.000Z","uid":75100,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e502e232c9adc2fd30d5d766fbc54917e175a22b","tid":936346,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"利申定先，呢個並唔係問症po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本人唔係中醫師，只係自學左幾年既愛好者，真係好鐘意入面既理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我相信連登都有咁既同志，或者甚至係中醫師，所以想召集下，大家一齊吹下水，分享下日常，甚至互相推介下好醫書咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能有人係睇台灣既JT叔叔，紫林中醫入坑<br />\n可能有人係火神派，崇尚補陽藥<br />\n可能有人係經方派，覺得仲景無敵<br />\n<br />\n大家可以一齊交流下，分享下醫案咁，或者互相考下病因咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945b995c685776daca0437eab51eb65378413327","tid":936346,"uid":146340,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:28:56.000Z","msg":"連登仔on99淨係識屌中醫架咋"},{"pid":"8ece22df534974728ad9a15049b2d24cbcd5944e","tid":936346,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:41:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 天氣凍了，又是補腎時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08704564d0ef8a50e064130b8a180a7cf48b9b93","tid":936346,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"得閒想同大家分享下一個好網，裹面好多中醫好書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分哂類，有傷寒金匱類，有分析藥材的，有醫論同醫案，有就咁睇病狀提供解決方法既，我都係度獲益良多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"http://www.zysj.com.cn/lilunshuji/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zysj.com.cn%2Flilunshuji%2Findex.html&d=9hmRhwtFAtlAEPAiNVSA8E4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BG